title: GoFundMe’s ‘attack’ on Canada’s Freedom Convoy shows dangers of big tech: ex-NY official - Fox Business
content:
1. GoFundMe’s ‘attack’ on Canada’s Freedom Convoy shows dangers of big tech: ex-NY official  Fox Business
  2. Canada 'Freedom Convoy': Ottawa police arrest 7, threaten charges for others caught bringing fuel to truckers  Fox News
  3. Canadian-style trucker protests spread throughout the world  Fox News
  4. Canada's Trucker Protest May Spread From Ottawa to US  Bloomberg
  5. Canada's truck convoy is a stunt  The Washington Post
  6. View Full Coverage on Google News
description: GoFundMe’s decision to remove the fundraiser for the trucker freedom protest in Ottawa is the latest example of big tech trying to shut down voices shunned by the left and is the “latest red flag that Silicon Valley’s power over us has to be stopped,” a former lieutenant governor of New York said.
